insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1163', 'arrow', '[æro]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=arrow', '{n.}++箭，矢**++箭状物，(形状、速度、用途等)似箭的东西**++箭号(即→)**++[复数，用作单数]掷镖游戏**++= broad arrow**{vt.}++以箭头指示(或标出)；以箭号表示**++箭一般地飞向并穿过(或飞速行进)：**{vi.}++如箭般地迅速行动(或飞速行进)：**++如箭般地迅速行动(或飞速行进)：**{n.}', '++The arrow stuck in the tree.**++这枝箭射插在树上。**++The pickerel would occasionally arrow the surface.**++小狗鱼偶尔会箭一般地跃出水面。**++So if the arrow of time is based on our consciousness and our ability to perceive it, then do people like you who understand it more fully experience time differently then the rest of us?**++如果时间之箭是基于我们的意识和感知它的能力，那么像你这样更充分地理解它的人与我们其他人相比是否有不同的时间体验？**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1164', 'clan', '[klæn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=clan', '{n.}++克兰(苏格兰高地人的氏族、部落)；(苏格兰高地人的)宗族**++氏族；部落**++(有共同利益或特点的)宗派，帮派；集团，社团；组织**++【人类学】同祖集团；亲族，家族**', '++I met a number of the senior Senoussi clan in Tripoli and have no doubt they would be ready to assume leadership of anti-Gadaffi forces.**++在的黎波里我遇见大量的高级赛怒西宗族的人，并且一点也不怀疑他们将准备建立反卡扎菲武装的领导力量。**++These towns and their villages were the inheritance of the tribe of Naphtali, clan by clan.**++这些城并属城的村庄就是拿弗他利支派按着宗族所得的地业。**++Corruption flourishes because the clan runs things for its own benefit.**++腐败猖獗是因为宗族统治只关心其自身利益。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1165', 'substantiate', '[səbstænʃɪet]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=substantiate', '{vt.}++证明，证实：**++使具体化，使实体化；实现：**++充实，加强；使有实质内容：**', '++Tracking reaching behavior or eye movements will be necessary to substantiate the findings, she adds.**++追踪到行为或者眼神移动将进一步证实这个结果，她补充说。**++The building will be used as a laboratory and educational facility to substantiate the Living Building Challenge.**++该建筑将被用作实验室和教育设施，以证实活建筑难题的可行性。**++A visit to a salon will substantiate these observations.**++一次在沙龙里的访问将证实这些观察资料。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1166', 'indecipherable', '[ɪndɪsaɪfrəbl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=indecipherable', '{adj.}++(密码等)破译不出的，不可破译的**++(字迹等)难以辨认的，模糊的，难懂的**', '++Linda mounted the spread-eagle chair and soonan indecipherable gray image appeared on the screen.**++琳达坐在椅子上，屏幕上很快显示出一个难以辨认的灰色图像。**++The language has also proven to be indecipherable, though according to its page on Abe Books, cryptologists have managed to decipher the numbering system.**++尽管密码专家根据其在Abe books上的书页，成功的破译了其文字编译体系，但仍无法解释这些文字的含义。**++My efforts at conversation with the driver resulted only in grunts and indecipherable phrases.**++我努力地和司机讲话，但结果只有咕哝声和无法辨认的只言片语。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1167', 'elongate', '[ɪlɔŋɡet]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=elongate', '{vt.}++把…拉长，使更长，使伸长，使延长：**++把…拉长，使更长，使伸长，使延长：**{vi.}++变得更长，伸长，延长；呈细长形状：**++变得更长，伸长，延长；呈细长形状：**{adj.}++[亦作 elongated]**++拉长的，伸长的，延长的，延伸的**++【植物学】(树叶等)细长的**', '++The extra length will help elongate a full face, making it appear more oval.**++长出来的头发会让圆脸有被拉长的效果，从而更形似鹅蛋脸。**++It has to be comfortable ... but it has to give the perfect shape and elongate the legs to the maximum.**++它必须要舒服……但是这就要求有完美的鞋型并且最大限度的拉长双腿。**++The dissipation units are built into a building’s structural skeleton. They are hydraulic cylinders that elongate and contract as the building sways, sapping the motion of energy.**++耗散单元嵌入到了建筑的骨架中，它们就是液压的圆筒，可以伸长来限制建筑物的摇摆，逐渐耗散运动的能量。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1168', 'sensation', '[sɛnseʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=sensation', '{n.}++感觉，知觉**++兴奋，激动；感动**++感觉能力**++兴奋状态**++轰动 **++引起轰动的事(或事物等)**', '++The new book has created a great sensation.**++这本新书引起了巨大轰动。**++Working with one@s head causes a sensation of hunger quite as much as muscular work.**++脑力劳动与体力劳动引起的饥饿感觉是完全一样的。**++This responsiveness to reward thus works like the desire for new sensation: It gets you out of the house and into new turf.**++这种对奖励的反应就像对新感觉的渴望一样在起作用：它让你走出家门进入新的活动领域。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1169', 'weightlessness', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=weightlessness', '{n.}{adj.}++无重量的，几乎无重量的**++失重的；不可称量的**', '++He loved thefeeling of weightlessness and the excitement and adventure of it all.**++不过他喜欢在水下失重的感觉和冒险时带给他内心的那种兴奋。**++Some of the equipment measures the effects of space conditions, such as apparent weightlessness, on biological specimens -- including the crew.**++其中一些设备用来测试太空环境（如明显的失重）对人体的影响——其生物样本包括乘组人员。**++"I@ve waited my whole life for this ... what I remember most was the feeling of weightlessness, both physically and emotionally," Fulmor said.**++富勒莫说：“这是我一直以来的梦想，我印象最深的是失重的感觉，身体和心理上都有（这种感觉）。”**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1170', 'shaman', '[ʃæmən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=shaman', '{n.}', '++Her skeleton was surrounded by animal remains, leading the researchers to conclude that she was a shaman—an interpretation that received a mixed reaction from archaeologists.**++因为她的骨架被动物的骸骨所包围，所以研究人员认为她是一个巫师—对此，考古学家们看法不一。**++She discovered plenty, and in the center of her fieldwork research, in the Yulin region of northern Shaanxi, bordering Inner Mongolia, even uncovered an only recently deceased shaman called Lei Wu.**++在她野外研究的中心，与内蒙接壤的陕西省玉林地区，她发现了大量的资料，甚至揭秘了一位在近期去世的名叫吴磊的萨满僧人。**++Here the fox assumes the roles of a shaman, a diviner, a sorcerer, and a Celestial being all at once.**++这里，狐狸承担了巫师、卜卦人和术士的角色，又一下子位列仙班。 年龄在获得变身力量中扮演着极为重要的作用。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1171', 'credence', '[kridns]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=credence', '{n.}++相信，信任；可靠(性)；可信赖；确实**++凭证；证书，证件**++【宗教】祭器台,置放圣餐的小桌[亦称作credence table,credenza]**++碗橱，餐具柜**', '++Ironically, then, whathelped to beat back Marxism also lent a kind of credence to its claims.**++讽刺的是，帮助击退马克思主义的，同时赋予它的主张一种信任。**++Rumours about vaccines quickly gain credence in the internet hothouse, with sites feeding off each other.**++随着网站之间的相互摄取，在热门网站接种疫苗的谣言迅速获得信任。**++Those who care about public reason are routinely shocked by opinion polls and surveys showing high levels of credence given to the idea of intelligent design.**++关注公众理性的人通常会被民意测验和调查所显示的对于‘智慧设计论’的高度信任所震惊。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1172', 'mystique', '[mɪstik]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=mystique', '{n.}++神秘性；神秘的气氛**++(技艺的)奥秘，秘诀**++秘密宗教仪式**', '++In that way he maintains a certain mystique.And she, too.**++这样一来他还有她都保有了一定的神秘性。**++But I can tell by the look in his eyes when he grazes my pubic bone with his wristwatch: this is it. He has some warped idea about the mystique.**++但当他戴的手表轻轻擦到我的耻骨时我通过他的眼神能看出：他对耻骨的神秘性产生了扭曲的想法。**++There is something in the veil… Some mystique, passion… I’m not really sure what it is, but I see beauty there.**++面纱背后有些东西……神秘，深情……我不确定那是神秘，但是我看到了蒙面女子的美。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1173', 'diviner', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=diviner', '{n.}++占卜者；先知**++有先见之明的人；预言家；推测者**++以占卜杖探水(或矿)的人**', '++To help find out if the moon has water, another LRO instrument, Diviner, will map the temperature of the moon@s surface so scientists can search for places where ice could exist.**++为了发现月球上是否有水，另一种称为"预言家"(Diviner)的LRO仪器将勘测仪器表明的温度，便于科学家搜索冰可能存在的地方。**++Diviner will provide back-up data for LRO@s other ice-sensitive instruments, identifying areas where positive signs of ice would not make sense because the temperature is too high.**++Diviner将向LRO的其它感测冰的仪器提供备用资料，可确定在某些地带某些表明冰存的迹象可能因温度太高而不可信。**++The Lunar Reconnaissance Orbiter (LRO) has conducted an ongoing survey of temperatures on the moon@s surface through its Diviner Lunar Radiometer Experiment.**++月球轨道探测器(LRO)正在通过它搭载的月球辐射计实验设备进行一项关于月表温度的调查。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1174', 'turbine', '[tɝbaɪn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=turbine', '{n.}', '++The steam is then used to drive a steam turbine, as in a normal steam plant.**++然后这些蒸汽用来推动蒸汽涡轮机，就像一般的蒸汽动力装置一样。**++It extends six legs into the seabed to stabilize itself before installation of the pylon on which each turbine sits.**++在安装每架涡轮机的支柱前，这艘安装船先将六条腿伸入海床中，以便稳定船只本身。**++A lot of these companies – like the wind turbine manufacturer I mentioned – are the foundation on which we can rebuild our economy to compete in the 21st century.**++很多这样的公司——就像我刚才所提到的风力涡轮机制造商——它们是我们重建在21世纪具有竞争性经济的基础。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1175', 'megawatt', '[mɛɡəwɑt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=megawatt', '{n.}', '++A megawatt is an instantaneous measure of power.**++一兆瓦是电力的瞬间衡量指标。**++Still, there is not a single megawatt of EGS-produced power on line yet, and, at best, it will be quite a while before it becomes a significant energy source.**++不过，EGS还没能向电网输送哪怕是一兆瓦的电力，就是按最好情况算，它要成为主要的能源来源还很需要一些时日。**++As the renewable technologies continued to mature, the report added, the cost per megawatt (MW) continued to fall.**++报道又说，因为可再生能源技术不断走向成熟，每兆瓦（MW）的成本继续下跌。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1176', 'electrocute', '[ɪlɛktrəkjut]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=electrocute', '{vt.}++使触电死亡：**++[美国英语]施以电刑，以电刑处死，尤指用电椅处死(罪犯)：**', '++The electrocute and disintegrate videos show it pretty well.**++瓦解之光和电刑的动画很好的显示了这一点。**++As it happens, a razor that is safe in Europe is unlikely to electrocute Americans.**++碰巧在欧洲使用安全的剃须刀不大可能使美国人触电身亡**++As it happens, a razor that is safe in Europe is unlikely to electrocute Americans. So, ask businesses on both sides of the Atlantic, why have two lots of tests where one would do?**++碰巧在欧洲使用安全的剃须刀不大可能使美国人触电身亡，因此，大西洋两岸的企业都在问，当一套测试可以解决问题时，为什么需要两套呢？**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1177', 'bead', '[bid]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=bead', '{n.}++(有孔的)小珠；玻璃珠，木珠，金属珠**++[复数](尤指天主教徒的)一串念珠**++[复数]串珠饰，穿孔挂饰，珠子项链**++(枪的圆形)准星，照星**++(水)珠；(水)泡；(血)滴，(尤指脸上的)汗珠**++(冒泡液体、酒、矿泉水等冒出的)气泡 **++(啤酒的)泡沫**{vt.}++用小珠装饰；用珠连成一串，把…像串珠子般连接起来，把…串成珠状，把…连成一串：**++缀珠状物于；在…上形成小珠，在…上面形成珠状物：**++【木工】在…作串珠饰**{vi.}++(尤指液体)结珠，形成珠状，成滴状：**++瞄准**', '++Since then the researchers have reduced the bead’s size to about 250 micrometres.**++自那以后研究者已经将珠子的尺寸减小到大约250微米。**++He shakes his head at the thought of this one thing, this single hideous bead on the necklace of his life.**++他一边思索着这件事一边摇着他的头，他生活的项链上唯独可怕的一颗珠子。**++An ispy jar - Fill the jar with rice and a few secret objects like a coin, a paperclip, a button, a bead, a small toy, dice, etc and have kids see if they can find all the treasures.**++瓶中寻宝 - 把瓶子装满大米，在里面藏一些小东西，比如一枚硬币，一个纸夹，一枚纽扣，一枚珠子，一个小玩具，一颗骰子等等。 让孩子找找，看他（她）们能不能找到宝物。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1178', 'crude', '[krud]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=crude', '{adj.}++生的，天然的，未加工的；未提炼的**++(意见等)不成熟的，初步的；肤浅的，幼稚的；简陋的**++粗糙的；生硬的；不完善的**++粗野的，缺乏教养的**++露骨的，不加掩饰的；赤裸裸的**{n.}++[美国英语](未加工的)天然物质； (尤指)原油 (= crude oil)**', '++Their daily work is to refine crude oil.**++他们每天的工作是精炼原油。**++Primitive man hunted wild animals with crude stone implements.**++原始社会的人用粗糙的石器猎取野兽。**++It is the future of media -- crude, simple, and missing loads of things we would want, yes, but new media always show up that way.**++这就是未来媒体的雏形：我们想知道但却错过的，粗糙的、简单的大量事件，新媒体通常都是这种种姿态出现。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1179', 'mammoth', '[mæməθ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=mammoth', '{n.}++【古生物】猛犸象(已绝种的一种长毛巨象)**++庞然大物**{adj.}++[美国英语]巨大的，庞大的**', '++One of the two mammoth museums.**++两个猛犸象博物馆中的一个。**++Any of them might conceal a mammoth graveyard or the next mummified Lyuba, they point out.**++牧民们指出，某个湖泊里就可能藏着猛犸象墓地或者下一个木乃伊一样的卢芭。**++Partial remains of five mastodons, three Ice Age bison and a juvenile Columbian mammoth, as well as plant matter and insects, have also been found.**++同时发现的还有五头乳齿象、三头冰河期野牛和一只少年哥伦比亚猛犸象的遗骸，以及植物和昆虫。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1180', 'derrick', '[dɛrɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=derrick', '{n.}++[亦作oil derrick](油井的)井架，油井塔，钻塔**++【机械学】塔式起重机；(尤指船用)吊杆式起货设备，起货桅；转臂起重机**++[美国俚语](偷窃贵重物品或商品的)小偷**{vt.,vi.}++【机械学】用转臂起重机移动(或吊起)**++[美国俚语]【棒球】使(投手)离场，替换(投手)**', '++Derrick: No. They always want to keep the cost down.**++戴里克：不雇，他们总想着降低成本。**++The expectation for Derrick Rose is that he become that guy.**++对罗斯的期待就是希望他成为那样的人物。**++@It@s almost a flight out of the dollar, @ said Mr. Derrick.**++迪瑞克说，这几乎可以说是一场“逃离美元的运动”。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1181', 'drilling pipe', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=drilling pipe', '{...}++...**', '++This year the US, EU and Argentina have started anti-dumping investigations into Chinese exports like oil drilling pipe and coated art paper.**++而新年伊始，美国、欧盟、阿根廷已相继对我国油井钻管、铜版纸等产品发起反倾销调查。**++Despite early hopes that the oil spill could be minimized, the rig@s fractured drilling pipe is currently leaking 42, 000 gal. of crude a day.**++由于钻油塔的管道断裂，每日漏油量为42 000加仑，人们本以为可以将溢油量控制在最小量的希望破灭。**++With a great development of petroleum industry in our country, the requirement of drilling pipe is not only big quantity but also good quality.**++随着我国石油工业的高速发展，对石油钻杆的需要不仅表现在数量上的增加，而且对钻杆的质量也提出了更高的要求。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1182', 'dismantle', '[dɪsmæntl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=dismantle', '{vt.}++拆除…的家园(或装备、装置、设备、防御工事等)：**++拆开，拆除，拆散，拆卸；解散：**++脱掉…的衣服；除掉…的覆盖物(of):**++取消；废除；摧毁；夷平：**{vi.}++(机器等)可拆卸，可拆开：**++(机器等)可拆卸，可拆开：**', '++Last year, North Korea began to dismantle that complex, where it runs a nuclear reactor and reprocess fuel rods to recover plutonium, but it vowed in June to restart production there.**++去年，朝鲜就开始拆除这个曾经那儿运行过核反应堆并为恢复钚重新准备燃料的基地，但是它在六月又发誓要在那儿重新开始生产。**++In response, Defense Minister Ehud Barak said he intends to dismantle 22 illegal settlement outposts in the West Bank.**++对于这个问题，国防部长巴拉克说，他打算拆除约旦河西岸的22个非法定居点。**++They may have served the country well when its population was young and growing, but now it needs to dismantle its rigid corporate hierarchies to allow new people and ideas to emerge.**++当人口还是年轻化和增长的时候，它们可能起到了很好的效果，但现在，需要取消这种死板的企业等级制度，从而允许新人和创新想法脱颖而出。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1183', 'refinery', '[rɪfaɪnəri]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=refinery', '{n.}', '++They fly over what looks like a small refinery.**++他们飞过一个看上去上个精炼厂的建筑。**++Those levels of emissions could increase the cancer risk to refinery employees and the public, she says.**++她说，那些未经控制的苯排放可以增加精炼厂员工和公众患癌症的风险。**++The blue whale had disappeared into these giant tanks, arranged in long rows as at any refinery.**++蓝鲸就消失在这些，和任何一座炼油厂一样，排成一长列的巨大的金属容器里。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1184', 'tanker', '[tæŋkɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=tanker', '{n.}++油轮，油船**++[美国英语]运油飞机；空中加油飞机**++= tank car**++=tank truck**++[口语]坦克手**++[美国俚语]酒精饮料运输车**{vt.}++用油轮等运输**', '++The oil was discharging from the tanker at the rate of thousands of gallons an hour.**++石油以每小时数千加仑的速度正从油轮中流出来。**++Oil from well leaks is much thicker than the processed oil that spills during tanker accidents.**++这些从油井中直接泄漏的油污比油轮事故中泄漏的成品油要稠密得多。**++The researchers are sharing their real-time data on whale locations, transmitted from the buoys via satellite, with tanker captains, who can then slow down their ships or alter course to avoid whales.**++研究人员正分享他们的实时数据去为鲸鱼定位，通过卫星与油轮船长从浮标传送数据，船长能放慢船速或改变航道来避开鲸鱼。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1185', 'slick', '[slɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=slick', '{adj.}++光滑的；有光泽的**++圆滑的，油滑的；口齿伶俐的**++狡猾的，狡黠的，诡诈的**++滑的，滑溜溜的**++精巧的，巧妙的；技术娴熟的，灵巧的**++(赛车车胎)花纹磨光的，磨平的**++(牧区牲畜)未烙印的，野的**++[口语]徒有虚名的，华而不实的；肤浅的**++[俚语]极好的，一流的**{adv.}++平滑地；润滑地；圆滑地**++熟练地，灵活地，巧妙地**++直接；恰好**{vt.}++使平滑，使光滑，使光亮：**++[美国口语]打扮，装扮；修饰(up):**++【制革】用刮刀刮(皮革等)**++【美国历史】经治安委员会批准后惩处**{vi.}++滑动，平滑地移动：**++打扮整齐，修饰(up):**', '++It is a good all-around loader, combining a slick user interface with a wealth of functionality.**++它是一个非常好的全面的加载程序，组合了灵活的用户界面和大量的功能。**++It features a heavy titanium timepiece mounted in a metal band, but you can ditch the band and put the timepiece in a slick pocket watch housing.**++它是一款沉重的钛手表配有一条金属带子，但你可以摘下带子直接将手表放进一个光滑的怀表口袋里。**++Do not be fooled by this slick ninja!**++别被这个狡猾的忍者所愚弄！**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1186', 'oil slick', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=oil slick', '{...}++...**', '++As the flood crested, an oil slick caught fire and burned our house down to the waterline.**++洪峰到来时，水面上的一层油膜不幸着火，把我家的房子吃水线以上部分全部烧塌。**++The oil slick is particularly visible in this image because of the way the sun reflects off the oil and the surrounding water.**++在这幅图像中你可以很明显地看到那片浮油，这是因为浮油和周围的海水对于阳光的反射有着很大的不同。**++The northwestern tip of the oil slick almost touches the Mississippi Delta.**++海面浮油西北方的尖端几乎触及密西西比三角洲。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1187', 'subside', '[səbsaɪd]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=subside', '{vi.}++下降，下沉，下陷；沉到底；沉淀：**++平静，平息：**++减弱，消退；消失，退落：**++[口语]坐下，跪下；躺下：**', '++The lees of wine gradually subside.**++酒渣慢慢地沉淀下来。**++After a few minutes,the amylum began to subside.**++几分钟之后，淀粉开始沉淀。**++Once the excitement, the motivation and the initial momentum subside (and they will), what will keep you doing what you need to do, to create the change you want to see in your world?**++人一旦兴奋，动机和最初的动力就会减弱（他们会这样），什么会让你保持做你要做的，去创造出这种在你的世界里你想看到的改变？**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1188', 'catastrophe', '[kətæstrəfi]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=catastrophe', '{n.}++戏剧(尤指悲剧)的结局[参较catastasis,epitasis, protasis]**++悲惨的结局；毁灭；覆灭**++骤然而来的大灾难、灾祸、祸患**++彻底的失败，大败，惨败**++【地质学】(地震等)灾变**++[亦称作catastrophe function]【数学】突变**', '++He is teetering on the edge of catastrophe.**++他在大灾难的边缘徘徊。**++Finally, we hope against hope that we have the courage to ensure that this type of catastrophe can be prevented or mitigated.**++最后，我们还是抱有一线希望，希望我们有勇气保证能够预防或者减轻这样的大灾难。**++A catastrophe is brewing.**++一场灾祸正在酿成。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1189', 'diameter', '[daɪæmɪtɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=diameter', '{n.}++直径**++径，对径**++【光学】透镜放大的倍数，放大率[略作d.，dia.或diam]**', '++It was an ugly dull orange, about a foot in diameter, and stuck up a couple of inches through the back lawn waiting to trip me .**++它外表丑陋，呈暗色橙形，直径大约有一英尺，有几英寸高凸起在屋后的草坪上，好像随时等着要绊倒我似的。**++Atlas, the flatter of the two, has a diameter of only 18 kilometres from pole to pole, but is almost 40 kilometres across its waist.**++阿特拉斯是两者中较平整的一个，从南极点到北极点的直径只有18公里，但是它的赤道周长却有40公里。**++Package instructions specify the correct depth for each variety, but the best general rule is the old one: seeds should be covered twice the depth of their own diameter.**++每个品种的包装说明上都特别强调正确的播种深度，但是最好的方法是古老的那个：播种的深度是种子直径的两倍。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1190', 'tentative', '[tɛntətɪv]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=tentative', '{adj.}++试验(性)的，尝试(性)的；暂时的**++踌躇的，犹豫不决的；没有把握的**{n.}++试验，尝试**', '++I use the word “tentative” here because these are more rough thoughts than a philosophy that I trust with certainty.**++我在这里使用了“暂定”这个词语是因为这些简单的粗糙思想肯定比高深哲学更能令人信服。**++While tentative, this science is telling us that each of us is a package composed of Mommy@s genes, Daddy@s genes and the bacterial genes that have moved in and stayed.**++试验的同时，这种科学也在告诉我们我们每一个人都是由母亲的基因、父亲的基因和进入或停留在体内的细菌的基因组成的基因包。**++To sum up, we are able to make some tentative plans about the future, all because the flexibility built into the iterative process allows us some deviation from the original plan.**++总之，我们能够制定一些未来的试验性计划，所有都是因为构建于迭代过程中的灵活性允许我们适当地偏离原来的计划。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1191', 'criterion', '[kraɪtɪriən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=criterion', '{n.}', '++Practice is the sole criterion of truth.**++实践是检验真理的惟一标准。**++Practice is the sole criterion of truth.**++实践是检验真理的唯一标准。**++Only social practice can be the criterion of truth.**++真理的标准只能是社会的实践。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1192', 'shooting gallery', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=shooting gallery', '{...}++...**', '++Because we sit in a cosmic shooting gallery, with 100 tons of material hitting us every day.**++因为我们位于宇宙射击场，每天有100吨的物质射向我们。**++I’ve never seen a dirty needle before, though I have worked in places where the bathroom was the local shooting gallery.**++尽管在当地射击场的浴室工作过，我还从来没有见过一个脏的针头。**++Your upcoming show at Shooting Gallery, “Wild Wild East” references the fusion of these cultures.**++你即将在射击场画廊举行的展览“苍凉狂野的东方”强调了这种文化的融合。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1193', 'notorious', '[notɔrɪəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=notorious', '{adj.}++臭名昭著的，声名狼藉的**++著名的；众所周知的**', '++The lawyer has defended some of the most notorious criminals.**++这名法官已为一些最臭名昭著的罪犯当过辩护律师。**++The celebrations were notorious enough that followers of Cybele were banished from Rome.**++臭名昭著的庆祝活动，以至于信徒之母的是从罗马放逐。**++He also compared the treatment of prisoners with that at the notorious Abu Ghraib prison in Iraq.**++同时他将对囚犯的治疗与伊拉克臭名昭著的阿布格莱布监狱相提并论。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1194', 'serpentine', '[sɝpəntin]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=serpentine', '{adj.}++蛇的**++似蛇的，蛇状的**++(道路等)弯弯曲曲的，蜿蜒的**++阴险的，狡猾的；奸诈的**{n.}++弯弯曲曲的东西；有如盘蛇状的东西**{vt., vi.}++(使)迂回曲折地前进**{n.}', '++This is a serpentine road going through the Urals.**++这是一条蜿蜒的路穿过乌拉尔山。**++For example, the marble hierarchy includes multiple peer-level types of marble, such as travertine, serpentine, and onyx.**++例如，大理石层次结构包括多种对等级别的大理石类型，例如石灰华、蛇纹石和缟玛瑙。**++Like those of China, Japan’s dragons are usually serpentine creatures with clawed feet and lack the wings of their European counterparts.**++像中国的龙一样，日本的龙通常是蜿蜒的动物，拥有可以爬行的腿，而没有欧洲龙的翅膀。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1195', 'omit', '[əmɪt]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=omit', '{vt.}++省略；删节；排除：**++遗漏；疏忽；忘记：**++[废语]无视；放弃**', '++So you can omit the schema location.**++因此您可以省略这个模式位置。**++If the procedure is unique, you can omit parameters that have default values and enter the parameters in any order.**++如果过程是惟一的，那么可以省略有默认值的参数，并且可以按任意顺序输入参数。**++You can omit this format information.**++您可以省略这一格式信息。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1196', 'concentration', '[kɑnsntreʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=concentration', '{n.}++集结，集中，聚集**++专注，专心**++浓度；密度；浓缩**++浓缩物；集中之物**', '++They liberated all war prisoners from the concentration camp.**++他们将所有战俘从集中营里解放出来。**++A gas in solution diffuses from a region of greater to one of less concentration.**++溶液中的气体会由浓度高的部分扩散到浓度低的部分。**++When you think with full and strong concentration about something that you want to happen, and your mind does not resist the subject of your thought, your thought materializes.**++当你用全部的、足够坚定的信念集中在你希望发生的事情上，以至于你的精神无法抵制你的这个想法，你的想法就实现了。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1197', 'remediation', '[rɪ,midɪeʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=remediation', '{n.}++[美国英语]【教育学】**++矫正；补救**++补习**', '++If you do find an infected machine, the jury is out about how best to do remediation.**++如果你在企业网络中发现了一台被感染的机器，那就应该考虑如何来最好的进行补救。**++Each machine also requires continued remediation and security patches to comply with security regulations.**++每台机器还需要不断的补救和安全性修补来符合安全法规。**++From the set of identified gaps, the analyst must determine the criticality of the gap, what data sources may address the gap (if any), and incorporate a remediation or mitigation plan for the gap.**++根据标识出的这组差异，该分析必须确定差异的临界点，什么数据源可以解决这个差异（如果有的话），并生成一个补救或迁移计划，以消除差异。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1198', 'smelter', '[smɛltɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=smelter', '{n.}++熔炼者，冶炼工**++冶炼厂主；冶铸工**++冶炼物**++冶炼厂；熔炉**', '++SMELTER: Some 3.8 million metric tons of lead are produced annually by separating it from mined ore using high heat.**++熔炉：每年约有380万公吨的铅是通过高温加热矿石的方法分离制造出来的。**++If refurbishment is not an option, reputable recyclers will use mechanical shredding and a high-tech separation device to take out the usable metals, which can then be sent to a smelter.**++如果不能翻新，有信誉的回收商将使用机器将旧电子设备打碎，用高技术分离设备提炼出有用的金属，这些金属可以送去冶炼厂。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1199', 'timescale', '[...]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=timescale', '{...}++...**', '++Another limitation is just the basic timescale inherent in the method definition.**++另一个局限是在方法定义中的基本时间单位。**++The project does not yet have a fixed timescale, although it was unlikely to produce anything physical for "at least five years".**++虽然这个项目在至少五年之内不可能生产出任何物质性的东西，但它它目前还没有固定的时标。**++But they described their estimates as conservative and warned a large-scale extinction would have an impact on a timescale beyond human imagining.**++但他们对自己的估量仍然描述的很保守，并且警告一次大范围的物种灭绝在时间尺度上的影响将会超出人们的想象。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1200', 'eukaryotic', '[]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=eukaryotic', '{adj.}', '++The first eukaryotic cells faced all three problems in spades.**++最早的真核细胞肯定直面过所有这三个难题。**++This overturns the traditional view that the jump to complex @eukaryotic@ cells simply required the right kinds of mutations.**++这颠覆了传统的观点，即实现复杂的@真核@细胞的跳跃发展仅仅要求正确种类的突变。**++What still needs to be explained is how the more typical eukaryotic phosphorylation cascades evolved and came to replace the bacterial systems.**++我们仍然需要解释的是更特化的真核生物的磷酸化途径是怎么进化而来并取代了细菌的系统。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1201', 'nuclei', '[njʊklɪ,ai]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=nuclei', '{n.}++nucleus的变形**{n.}++核，核心，中心**++起头，开始**++【核子学】核**++【化学】(晶)核，环**++【植物学】籽仁**++【生物学】细胞核**++【解剖学】神经核**++【天文学】(慧)核**++【气象学】(水汽)凝结核**', '++To free electrons, something has to make them whirl fast enough to break away from their nuclei.**++为了释放电子，必须使电子高速旋转而足以摆脱原子核的束缚。**++When neutrinos interact with electrons or nuclei of those water or oil molecules, they give off a flash of light that sensors can detect.**++当中微子与那些水分子或油分子的电子或原子核相互作用时，会发出传感器可以检测到的闪光。**++Thus we see that ideas are embryonic thoughts, nuclei of spirit-substance from the inner worlds.**++这样，我们看到，这些想法都是一些雏形，来自内在世界的精神实质的核心。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1202', 'diversification', '[dɪ,vɝsɪfɪkeʃən]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=diversification', '{n.}++【商业】(投资的)经营多样化，多样化的经营**++(一地区企业)布局多样化**++多样化，形形色色**', '++This is remarkable considering the tremendous diversification benefits the metal can provide for an investment portfolio.**++这是很明显的，金属可以为投资组合提供巨大的多样化的好处。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1203', 'locale', '[lokæl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=locale', '{n.}++(事件发生的)现场，地点，场所**++(电影、戏剧等的)背景；故事发生场所[亦作 local ／ləukɑ:l∥-kæl／ ]**', '++Then we can pass along the locale object with each child thread initiation.**++这样我们将可以传递实现每一个子线程初始化的场所对象。**++Therefore, how to enable globalization is about how to work with the locale.**++因此，怎样实现全球化归根结底就是怎样处理场所。**++A general solution for the problem above is to have each user thread hold a locale variable by passing the variable to the user thread during its construction.**++对于以上问题通用的解决方法，是通过在构造变量期间将其传递给用户线程，来让每一个用户都有一个场所变量。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1204', 'unassignable', '[]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=unassignable', '{...}++...**', '++...**++...**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1205', 'cylinder', '[sɪlɪndɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=cylinder', '{n.}++【几何学】圆柱，柱体；柱(面)**++圆柱形物；圆筒，量筒，烘筒**++(左轮手枪的)旋转弹膛**++(泵的)机筒，泵体**++(发动机的)汽缸；液压缸；(液压操纵的)油缸**++(印刷机的)滚筒；轮转机的滚筒**++【考古学】(雕有楔形文字的)圆柱形石(或陶器)**++【计算机】磁道**++【纺织业】(提花机)花筒，印花铜滚筒；针筒**{vt.}++给…装配汽缸(或滚筒)**++使受汽缸(或滚筒)的作用**', '++The piston is reciprocating inside cylinder.**++活塞在汽缸内部往复运动。**++You see a green cylinder with a clock next to it while you create this array.**++在创建此阵列时，您会看到一个绿色的圆筒，旁边还有一个时钟。**++They sit in rows, taking hot glass into their gloved hands and spinning it around a cylinder.**++他们成排坐着，用戴着手套的手拿起炽热的玻璃，将它绕在一个圆筒上。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1206', 'condenser', '[kəndɛnsɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=condenser', '{n.}++冷凝器，冷却箱；凝汽室；凝气机；制冷装置**++压缩器**++【光学】聚光器，聚光镜**++【电工学】电容器**++聚合器；缩合器**', '++The ammonia circulates through a condenser and then an evaporator, where it provides the cooling, before being reabsorbed by the water.**++氨经冷凝器后流入蒸发器，在这里它在被水再次吸收之前提供制冷效果。**++The evaporator helps cool the air, the condenser helps ready the system@s refrigerant for the cooling process, and the compressor helps move refrigerant back and forth between them.**++蒸发器有助于冷却空气，冷凝器帮助准备冷却过程中的制冷剂，压缩机有助于制冷剂在它们之间移动来回。**++In your fractional distillation condenser.**++或在分馏冷凝器。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1207', 'rotary', '[rotəri]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=rotary', '{adj.}++旋转的；转动的**++有旋转部件的；有旋转叶片的**++(人员)轮换的，轮流的**++使用于旋转式机器的**{n.}++旋转式机器(或发动机)**++[R-][美国英语] =Rotary Club**++[美国俚语] =traffic circle**++【电工学】 =synchronous converter [亦作rotary converter]**', '++The rotary chair is used to assess middle ear injury of soldiers who may have experienced a concussion.**++这是一张旋转椅，可以用来评估战场上遭受震荡而中耳损伤的士兵情况。**++The MK54 is a free swimming torpedo launched from rotary and fixed wing aircraft, and surface ships.**++Mk54是一种从旋转与固定翼飞机以及水面船只上发射的自由航行鱼雷。**++As a result, bacteria have developed a unique way of swimming: using tiny rotary motors called flagella, which resemble corkscrews.**++结果细菌进化出独特的游泳方式：使用叫做鞭毛的像螺旋开瓶器的微型旋转马达。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1208', 'flicker', '[flɪkɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=flicker', '{vi.}++(如蜡烛在风中)闪烁(不定)，闪动；忽隐忽现，明灭不定：**++摇曳，摇动，晃动；(旗帜等)飘动；来回晃动：**++(鸟)振翼，振翅**++(急速地)瞥视**++[美国俚语]昏倒；假装昏倒**{vt.}++使摇曳，使晃动；使闪烁不定，使颤动：**++使摇曳，使晃动；使闪烁不定，使颤动：**{n.}++扑动，摇曳，闪烁，忽隐忽现，明灭不定**++闪光，火花，火星**++速来速去的动作，轻快的动作；闪现，闪动**++[美国俚语]电影，好莱坞制作业的绰号[通常用于复数]**++[美国俚语]假装昏倒的乞丐**++【计算机】(在光栅扫描显示中的)闪烁**{n.}', '++Push "H" key , a single color move to flicker , push once more , cut from one color to another .**++按H键，就会变成单独一种颜色闪烁，再按一下，就会从一种颜色转换成另一种颜色。**++Shadows from the campfire outside flicker on the tent as you feast on an Arabian barbecue buffet.**++当你好好享用一顿阿拉伯烤肉自助餐，外面营火的影子在帐篷上闪烁**++The rub is that whereas there is little to confuse with a flicker of light in dark benthic recesses, any movement whatever will produce sounds.**++而声学探测的缺陷在于，尽管在黑暗的深海底没有什么会干扰到闪烁光，但是任何动静都可能发出声响。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1209', 'furnace', '[fɝnɪs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=furnace', '{n.}++炉子，火炉；熔炉；蒸汽炉**++极灼热的地方；[比喻]火炉**++严峻的考验；[比喻]熔炉**{vt.}++【冶金学】把(金属)放在炉中加热**', '++It was hot summer and at the edge of the desert it was like a furnace.**++那是一个炎热的夏天，在沙漠的边缘，天热得像火炉一样。**++Seconds later, there was a loud whooshing sound, "like somebody turned the furnace on, " Gonzales recalls, and his truck was ablaze.**++几秒后，他突然听到响亮的嘶嘶声，他回想到“像是有人打开了火炉。 这时他的卡车已经着火了。**++The main space in the train cars is taken up by the steam generator with various valves, nozzles, manometers and a huge furnace.**++这辆车头的主要部分都被一台蒸汽机占据着，蒸汽机有一堆的阀门，喷口，压力计和庞大的火炉**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1210', 'turnpike', '[tɝnpaɪk]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=turnpike', '{n.}++高速公路**++= tollgate**++turnpike road**++【历史、军事】(防御用)鹿砦，鹿寨**++【历史】收税栅；通行费卡门**++收费公路**++[废语] = turnstile**', '++We@re on the turnpike.just two miles from downtown.**++我们就在高速公路上——离市区只有两英里。**++Similar results were achieved in Finland and on the New Jersey Turnpike.**++在芬兰和新泽西收费公路得出类似的结果。**++But how does this help me when someone cuts me off on the New Jersey Turnpike?**++但当有人突然在我们通往新泽西州的收费公路上被阻挡了，这有什么帮助呢？**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1211', 'laden', '[ledn]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=laden', '{adj.}++满载的，装满的**++负担过重的；心情沉重的；使苦恼的**{vt.,vi.}', '++They moor their laden boats near my trees.**++他们把满载的船只拴在我的树上。**++Who might take over if bin Laden finally does go?**++那么要是本拉登最终离去后，谁会上位呢？**++There are going to be some folks who deny it. The fact of the matter is, you will not see Bin Laden walking on this earth again.**++因此是否存在照片并不会有任何的差别，肯定会有人否认这一事实，但事实是你将不会在这地球上看到本拉登。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1212', 'flange', '[flændʒ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=flange', '{n.}', '++Then tighten the nut on the drain body, sealing the gasket and washer against the drain flange.**++然后紧上存水弯的螺丝，密封排水法兰相应的垫圈和垫片。**++BP began trying Saturday afternoon to remove the bolted top flange that only partially completed the seal with the old cap.**++英国石油公司在星期六下午开始尝试拆除用来固定旧防漏帽的法兰，这种旧的防漏帽不能充分实现堵漏功能。**++The flange also ensures that there will always be some water left in the tank (about half an inch) to prevent the black plastic from melting.**++法兰盘的高度应该有半英寸，以确保水箱总能存有一定的水，使黑色塑料膜不至于熔化。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1213', 'rudimentary', '[,rudɪmɛntri]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=rudimentary', '{adj.}++基本的；初期的**++发育不完全的，未成熟的**++退化的[亦作rudimental]**', '++The analysis of log data can be rudimentary, such as simple summaries of basic activity.**++对日志数据的分析可能只是初步的，例如基本活动的简单总结。**++The tracing capabilities that are implemented are rather rudimentary, but will be sufficient for our purposes.**++已实现的跟踪功能是相当基本的，但是对于我们的目的来说足够了。**++Free source control tools, and the homegrown systems based on them, provide only rudimentary support for checking files in and out.**++免费控制工具，以及在它们基础上自行开发的系统，只为检查文件的输入输出提供了初步的支持。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1214', 'roam', '[rom]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=roam', '{vi.}++闲逛；漫步；漫游；徘徊；流浪：**++(有目的地)走来走去:**{vt.}++在…漫步；在…徘徊：**++在…漫步；在…徘徊：**{n.}++闲逛；漫游；徘徊**', '++I like to roam around the fields.**++我喜欢在田野中漫步。**++The rover should have at least one Martian year, or 687 days on Earth, to roam the planet, during which time it will collect, grind and analyze around 70 samples of rock and soil.**++火星科学实验室至少要在火星上漫步一个火星年或者说687个地球日的时间，在其间它将收集、研磨并分析70个左右的岩石和土壤样品。**++I want to roam about and see all the wide world, yet I also yearn for a little sheltered nook; like a bird with its tiny nest for a dwelling, and the vast sky for flight.**++我想到处漫游，饱览这个广大的世界，然而，我也渴望一个小小的隐蔽处所；像一只飞鸟，拥有一个微小的巢穴栖息，也想翱翔于浩瀚的天空。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1215', 'ubiquitous', '[jubɪkwɪtəs]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=ubiquitous', '{adj.}', '++Theory and some observational data pointed to the likelihood that they were ubiquitous.**++理论和一些观测数据则指向他们曾经普遍存在的可能性。**++We are gradually beginning to realize that the potential for life is ubiquitous throughout our galaxy.**++我们慢慢开始意识到生命的可能性在我们的银河中乃是普遍存在的。**++Taking this one step further, is life also ubiquitous in the multiverse? There are both zero and infinite answers to that question.**++由此更进一步说，生命在多元宇宙中也是普遍存在的吗？这一问题既没有答案，也有无穷多个答案。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1216', 'scanty', '[skænti]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=scanty', '{adj.}++少量的，不多的**++不足的，缺乏的；勉强的**++狭小的，狭窄的**++稀疏的，稀少的**++吝啬的；过分节约的**{n.}++= scanties**', '++The farmer @s financial difficulties were caused By a scanty harvest.**++这个农民的经济困难是因为收成不足造成的。**++Rivers coursing down from the mountains provide water for agriculture in a region of scanty rainfall.**++从这座山上流下来的河流为这降水量极少的地区提供了农业用的水源。**++There are many opinions on this subject; however, data on the potential health risks of GMO foods are scanty, which has made it impractical to draw conclusions from it up till now.**++关于这个主题有许多观点;然而 数据对潜在的健康风险的转基因食品是少之又少 从它直至目前为止 这使得不切实际得出结论.**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1217', 'sibling', '[sɪblɪŋ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=sibling', '{n.}++兄弟；姊妹；同胞**++【人类学】(血统)民族成员**++【生物学】姊妹株，姊妹体 **++【动物学】一母同胞**{adj.}++兄弟的；姊妹的；亲如兄弟(或姊妹)的**', '++On that day, you became the child of someone and the sibling of others.**++从那天开始，你就成为某个人的孩子，并且有了兄弟姐妹。**++Family jealousy: Sibling rivalry is one trademark characteristic of this type of jealousy.**++家庭嫉妒： 兄弟姐妹间的竞争是这类嫉妒的主要特征。**++The same link between sibling sex and offspring sex was not found for women.**++这种兄弟姐妹性别和孩子性别的联系，在女人方面却没有发现。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1218', 'plausible', '[plɔzəbl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=plausible', '{adj.}++似乎有理的；似乎可能的；表面上讲得通的**++似乎可靠的；似乎可信的**++巧嘴的，花言巧语的，会说话的**', '++But what if your mother and I created an environment where you would grow up to have a more plausible career than your dad?**++但是如果事我和你的妈妈给你创造了一个比你爸爸更好的生长环境，使你可以有一个更合理的职业生涯呢？**++Though they can@t yet prove that this is what happened on Mars, it seems like a plausible explanation, and doesn@t require water for the reddening process.**++虽然他们目前还不能证实这就是在火星上所发生的事情，但这似乎是一个很合理的解释，且变红的过程并不需要水的参与。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1219', 'infantile', '[ɪnfəntaɪl]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=infantile', '{adj.}++婴儿的，幼儿的；婴儿期的**++似婴儿的；幼稚的；孩子气的**++早期的，初期的**++(地形学上)幼年期的**', '++Is there a way to remedy this infantile behaviour?**++有什么办法改变他这种幼稚的行为吗？**++So I@m glad I didn@t give into that infantile, juvenile interest in facial, beauty and sex appeal.**++所以我很高兴我没有把我幼稚的，年轻的兴趣都放在脸的美丽和性的吸引上。**++I believe that much of this is native idiocy: the infantile blathering of people who have no idea how to engage in debate.**++我相信其中大部分属于与生俱来的愚蠢言论——那些不知道应该怎样加入讨论的人的幼稚胡话。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1220', 'amnesia', '[æmniʒə]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=amnesia', '{n.}', '++We tend to think that a person who is a complete victim of amnesia is still the same person as before.**++我们倾向于认为，一个彻底的健忘症患者，他与以前没有患病时仍然是同一个人。**++She also subscribed to a selective amnesia: “I have the habit of forgetting what I do not care to remember, ” she conceded.**++另外，她有选择性的健忘症：“我有个习惯，我会忘记那些我不想记住的事物，”她承认说。**++Amnesia is a primitive, self-preservation mechanism, which comes into play when man need to protect himself or herself from some form of severe emotional or physical trauma.**++健忘症是一种原始的自我保护心理，当人类需要从某种严重的感情或者是生理创伤进行自我保护的时候，它就会起作用。**');
insert into TOEFLWordBook values ('1221', 'toddler', '[tɑdlɚ]', 'http://dict.youdao.com/dictvoice?audio=toddler', '{n.}++学步的孩子；走路不稳的儿童；蹒跚行走的人**++[戏谑语]散步的人，漫步的人；信步走的人**++[常用作定语]童装尺码**', '++You control it by touching the screen — an intuitive interface that even a toddler can figure out.**++你通过触摸屏幕控制它-一个直观的界面甚至一个三岁小孩也能控制它。**++Ever since his dad let him tag along on road trips as a toddler, Gonzales had been fascinated by big trucks.**++自从他的父亲让他在公路之旅中像一个学步的小孩一样跟在其后，他就已经着迷于大卡车了。**++In the US, there have been 109 confirmed cases and only one fatality and that was a Mexican toddler who had travelled to the US after becoming infected.**++在美国，109认为被确诊患病，但是只有一例死亡，而且这仅有的一例也是墨西哥的一个婴儿，他在被感染后施行到了美国。**');
